<h1><%= t ".password_reset" %></h1>

<p>To reset your password click the link below:</p>

<%= link_to t(".password_reset"), edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %>

<p>This link will expire in two hours. If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is.</p>
